title: Welcome Home to Park Place! Just steps away from Downtown MV!
posting_body: ['Park Place: Apartments in Downtown Mountain View', 'CALL:', 'show contact info', 'x380', 'From $4,411', '.', '2 Bed 2 Bath .', '930 Sq.Ft', 'Park Place', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Address:', '851 Church Street Mountain View, CA 94041', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Park Place is offering this beautiful 2 bedroom 2 bathroom home with an open floor plan and wonderful hardwood flooring for immediate move in.', 'This home first introduces you to the living room with tall sliding doors leading you to the private deck.', 'On the opposite side, the dining room is paired with recessed lighting that also shines throughout the living area.', 'The kitchen offers a walk-in pantry and plenty of cabinet space with a full display of appliances.', 'The master bedroom in connected to a private bathroom, while both the bedrooms offer a great amount of closet space.', 'Its attractions speak for themselves when you are just a short walk away from downtown Castro St and so many options for public transportation like the San Antonio Caltrain.', 'Falling for Park Place already?', 'For more information contact the Park Place leasing staff.', 'LEASE\u2002\u2002TERMS', 'Variable', 'OFFICE\u2002 \u2002HOURS', 'Monday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Tuesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Wednesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Thursday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Friday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Saturday', '9:00am to 5:00pm', 'Sunday', '9:00am to 5:00pm', 'CALL US TODAY!', 'show contact info', 'x380', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
